						<summary><p>A <title xml:lang="ta">Pāratam</title>, that is, a Tamil version of an episode of the <title xml:lang="sa">Mahābhārata</title>.</p>

<p>The bundle is in disorder at the end and the beginning on Gallica photographies. The text transcription is given below with a tentative reordering of the folios.</p>
<p>Several folios with one page darker = outside page at some point of time.</p>

<p>Description based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>      

</summary>

